SYKES, Appellant, v. TEMPLE, Respondent (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 15, 1893.) Action by Byron H. Sykes against Abram Temple.

Argued before MAYHAM, P. J., and PUTNAM and HERRICK, JJ.

No opinion. Motion denied, with costs. For decision on appeal, see 23 N. Y. Supp. 425.
